Hey, man, I wanna go home.

1070
01:13:50,526 --> 01:13:52,858
Okay, son.
I'll help you.

1071
01:13:52,928 --> 01:13:55,624
- Please! The line!
- Okay.

1072
01:13:55,697 --> 01:13:58,359
All right.
Where'd he go?

1073
01:13:58,434 --> 01:14:00,026
No. No.

1074
01:14:00,102 --> 01:14:01,899
I don't know where he is.

1075
01:14:01,970 --> 01:14:03,733
I'll get you down.
I'll help you.

1076
01:14:03,806 --> 01:14:05,774
[Yelling]

1077
01:14:08,811 --> 01:14:10,608
[screaming]

1078
