Don't worry about it.
I'll take care of it.

1111
01:16:42,531 --> 01:16:43,793
[Phone chimes]

1112
01:16:46,468 --> 01:16:49,130
We can handle it.

1113
01:16:53,308 --> 01:16:56,505
[Phone ringing]

1114
01:17:02,618 --> 01:17:03,846
[thud]

1115
