about you, all right?

1119
01:17:35,350 --> 01:17:37,580
I don't know if this whole
sending the chain letter things

1120
01:17:37,653 --> 01:17:39,416
to you was a good idea.

1121
01:17:39,488 --> 01:17:41,456
Just call me back as soon
as you get this, all right?

1122
01:17:41,523 --> 01:17:44,117
If not, I'll be there
early in the morning.

1123
01:17:44,192 --> 01:17:46,160
[Beeps]

1124
