01:21:44,933 --> 01:21:47,493
Crenshaw has it set up so that
all the e-mails are going

1147
01:21:47,569 --> 01:21:50,504
to some police computer that checks them.
[Echoing continues]

1148
01:21:50,572 --> 01:21:51,732
[muffled gasping]

1149
